column2: Windy while sampling.  The rain gauge reading from 7/14-7/31 is 4.2 inches.
Very dry-lake very low the creek isn't even running
Summer has been very windy on the weekends-today is light breeze with ripples on the surface and it is overcast.
This has been a very cool- dry- windy summer.  Virtually no rain.  The creek has not run all summer.  Today is very sunny and clean
Been a very warm- early spring so lake appears more like an August lake
Windy in the west basin so secchi was altered- I am sure

Cool spring and early summer.  Had two very hot days this week.  Lots of rain this spring Been very sunny and hot- Lots of boat traffic this past weekend so the lake is stirred up. Been a very cool- wet spring and early June--we have had twso very hot days this week Been a very busy weekend on the lake with lots of boat traffic.  Lake is probably stirred up.  Very nice weather--warm and clear.   Busy boating weekend so the lake may be churned up--Good weather and clear sky
A beautiful day but a little breezey from the ESE--waves but no whitecaps
Very hot week--little overcast  Slight chop
Lake looks great- clear- breezy and choppy
Lake looks great- partly cloudy- gentle wind and choppy
Hot- clear and sunny- SW wind and choppy
Had a cool- late spring.  There has been lots of snow melt and spring rain.  Because of Memorial Day weekend- there has been a lot of boat traffic.
Mostly sunny day-some clouds; slight chop on the water; warm
80 degrees; we have had lots and lots of rain; lake surface is choppy
Ver breezy- had trouble holding our position; choppy; lots of algae; cloudy; Deer Lake does not look like itself
SW wind (5-10 mph); choppy;  overcast sky
Cloudy day; East breeze;  cloudy but warm
Mix of sun and clouds; Easterly breeze yet calm here because of land structure; warm
We have had warm days and coolish nights; today is overcast-no clear sun; light breeze so there is a slight chop on the water.
Continuing with warm (80s) days and coolish nights; overcast again; rain is predicted
partly cloudy- mild day; breezy from the east; lake is a bit choppy
Warm day-  week has had storms and winds
cool temp of 62- cloudy-  mild wind
Cloudy- moderate wind Cloudy- moderate wind Cloudy- moderate wind
light wind- cloudy light wind- cloudy light wind- cloudy
